      "_id": "page.future-resources---content--2",
      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## Speak to someone about the problem ##\r\n\r\n### Citizens Advice ###\r\n\r\nCitizens Advice provide information and guidance on housing problems online. You can also chat with an adviser online, call their helpline, or visit one of their face-to-face centres.\r\n\r\nAdviceline (England): 0800 144 8848\r\n\r\nAdvicelink (Wales): 03444 77 20 20\r\n\r\n### Shelter ###\r\nShelter provides advice and support to people with housing issues of all kinds. \r\n\r\nHelpline: 0808 800 4444"
    },
